tweet: OK, I've got some followers. I guess I had better say Aloha to everyone and thanks for joining me here at Twitter. More about me to follow.
After a 2+ month business trip, I will soon be back in Honolulu. Have been to - Japan, Hong Kong, Vietnam, Thailand, Singapore, Burma, Laos.
Am currently on my last stop which is Qingdao, China.  Been a looong trip.
Still on my traveling around Asia.  Looks like I will miss the July forth fireworks this year  ;-(
Forth of July in the USA and Honolulu.  Kind of sad, the fireworks is a bit boring but I'll still miss seeing it this year.
